data.description: Welcome to this charming and well maintained modular home pleasantly situated on approximately 7.6 acres m/l of unrestricted land. This three bedroom, three full bath home features a functional split bedroom floor plan with finished basement offering two separate living areas that provide ample space for a growing family or entertaining family and friends. This home also boast vasts amounts of storage space and an abundance of natural lighting. The master bedroom is expansive and includes a walk in closet, large bathroom with jetted tub, skylight, walk-in shower and double vanity countertop and sinks. The kitchen/dining combination is an ideal space for preparing family meals, baking or simply enjoying a favorite beverage and conversation with loved ones. Also worth mentioning in the kitchen, is a newer Bosch dishwasher, a new faucet and pantry for food storage. Additionally, there is a suitable area right off of the kitchen that would be a perfect space for formal dining. This well cared for home has been thoughtfully upgraded with newer carpet, newer interior paint and fresh stain on the wrap-around, deck which adds an inviting feeling to the home. Additional upgrades worth noting include: A NEW Frigidaire Gallery stove/oven, NEW fiberglass front door with frame, NEW locks and door knobs (inside & out) with programmable features. There are new ceiling fans & light fixtures too. What's more, is the homeowners added a sediment and carbon block water filtration system to help ensure clean and refreshing water throughout the home. Lastly, there is a new pressure tank, pressure switch in the well house, as well as, a new electrical breaker box with an added GFCI outlet servicing both the well house and heat pump. The homeowners also added risers to the septic system for easy accessibility.
